Package: offlineimap
Version: 3.99.6
Revision: 1
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Depends: python (>= 2.2)
BuildDepends: python (>= 2.2)
Source: %n_%v.tar.gz
SourceDirectory: %n-%v
CompileScript: python setup.py build
InstallScript: <<
  python setup.py install --prefix=%i
  install -d -m 755 %i/etc
  install -c -m 640 offlineimap.conf %i/etc/
  install -d -m 755 %i/share/doc/man/man1
  install -c -m 644 offlineimap.1 %i/share/doc/man/man1/
<<
ConfFiles: %p/etc/offlineimap.conf
DocFiles: COPYING COPYRIGHT ChangeLog README manual.*
Description: IMAP caching system
Homepage: http://quux.org/devel/offlineimap/
License: GPL
